{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/logo.png?t=1732950788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Want to make 3D models but don't know where to start? picoCAD is here to help! Focused on the bare essentials of 3D modelling, picoCAD blends simplicity with creativity, letting you make low-poly 3D models with just a few clicks. Whether you are a total beginner, or an expert, picoCAD is a unique and approachable tool to express your art in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/spinning_lorry.gif?t=1732950788\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/spinning_sub.gif?t=1732950788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Focused toolset:</strong> Create retro-style models without any prior experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Low-poly aesthetics:</strong> Capture the charm of early 3D games with pixelated models</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Texture mapping:</strong> Adding your own textures allows for endless experimentation and expression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Intentionally limited</strong>: A tight feature set and limited space focuses creativity where it matters most</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ready for games &amp; art:</strong> Export models (GIF, OBJ, MTL) to use in projects or showcase them in your portfolio</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Friendly community:</strong> Join our every growing discord community of artists and designers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/vehicles.gif?t=1732950788\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GOOD TO KNOW</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">picoCAD is built on the PICO-8 fantasy console and comes rich with constraints. Experiment to find your own workflow and anything is possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">checkout  for tutorials and examples!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">picoCAD is a standalone application and you don't need pico8 to run it.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make sure to read the manual and check out the tutorials</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/toaster_0.gif?t=1732950788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732950788","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732950788","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732950788","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732950788","content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800590/extras/logo.png?t=1732950788\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Want to make 3D models but don't know where to start? picoCAD is here to help! Focused on the bare essentials of 3D modelling, picoCAD blends simplicity with creativity, letting you make low-poly 3D models with just a few clicks. Whether you are a total beginner, or an expert, picoCAD is a unique and approachable tool to express your art in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st